{
  "3288190": {
    "name": "NumX",
    "steam_appid": 3288190,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288190/extras/965f8833e4afa1741f46366becd81b79.avif?t=1730958526\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>NumX is back!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After 2 years, NumX is back with an improved version. Rediscover old mini-games and discover new ones, alone or with friends, in the same room or on the other side of the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New game modes are also planned to bring a new experience around the mini-games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original NumX content such as old skins and music will also make a comeback.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288190/extras/38917de12034490277ef14fe33a2fc39.avif?t=1730958526\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NumX is a party-game containing several mini-games that can be played alone or with others, in which you play as a simple cube. And yes, sometimes simplicity is best. You can play online with a friend, or locally on the same computer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288190/extras/2dfc7745b926dbc0833c4dff0d0cfd14.avif?t=1730958526\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NumX has a variety of minigames that you can play such as :</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival VS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In VS Survival your goal is to avoid the grey cube for as long as possible!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Air Hockey</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Air Hockey, you have to be the first team to score 5 goals to win the game !</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obstacles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Obstacles, you have to avoid the obstacles that appear so that they don't push you into the water!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more...!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288190/extras/f2c13183b527eb851dd4d4e2a9d7b93f.avif?t=1730958526\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In NumX, you can play with up to 4 friends locally or online and compete for victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each player can play on the same keyboard or connect their controller!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288190/extras/441f655f8e77406f20c8b7a0b433f1eb.avif?t=1730958526\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you decide to play NumX minigames alone you will be awarded coins at the end of each game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With coins you can buy skins to customize your cube, backgrounds for the play frame, titles to display on your profile or emojis to use while playing online! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During events that are sometimes held, you even win double the amount of coins, so make use of them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288190/extras/adbde28b16fa6ea77d88d60e9552300a.avif?t=1730958526\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We hope you will have fun on NumX!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288190/extras/d79cd08bfc34238371564687c2086cbd.avif?t=1730958526\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p>",
